import matplotlib.pyplot as plt


t = np.arange(0, 1, 0.01)
y = 7*t**2 + 5

y_noise = y + np.random.randn(len(y))

pf_1 = np.polyfit(t,y_noise,2)

plt.plot(t, y_noise,label='x')
plt.plot(t, pf_1[0]*t**2 + pf_1[1]*t + pf_1[2],label='polyfit')
plt.legend(fontsize = 20)
